      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering power through a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. The M96 powerplant benefits from documented IMS bearing and rear main seal intervention, ensuring mechanical longevity and peace of mind. Suspension geometry remains tight with factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, providing the precise tactile feedback and telepathic steering response synonymous with the 911 platform. Finished in Arctic Silver over black leather, the interior maintains structural integrity with minimal bolster wear. This is a driver-focused example with a linear power band and a robust chassis, ready for spirited canyon carving or high-speed touring.",
